<section id="nucleo" class="swiss-section bg-[#d3d2bf] overflow-hidden">
  <div class="ink-splatter -left-10 bottom-4 opacity-20"></div>
  <div class="swiss-container grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-y-12">
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:pr-10 fade-up">
      <div class="swiss-kicker">01 / Filosofía / 思想</div>
      <p class="zine-jp text-6xl md:text-8xl mb-5 leading-none" aria-hidden="true">機能<br />美学</p>
      <h2 class="swiss-heading">Función y forma, <span class="swiss-accent">sin concesiones.</span></h2>
      <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md border-l-4 border-black pl-4">
        Cada decisión visual debe orientar. Cada decisión técnica debe sostener el negocio.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-7 lg:border-l-[3px] border-black lg:pl-10 fade-up">
      <div class="zine-panel relative p-3 md:p-5 bg-[#e9e8d8] -rotate-[0.4deg]">
        <div class="absolute -top-5 right-4 zine-label rotate-2">SYSTEM MAP / 構造</div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-4 min-h-80 md:min-h-[30rem] border-2 border-black">
          <div class="col-span-1 border-r-2 border-black p-3 md:p-5 flex flex-col justify-between bg-zt-primary text-white halftone">
            <span class="relative z-10 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">Input / 01</span>
            <strong class="relative z-10 font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-none">RAW<br />DATA</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="col-span-2 border-r-2 border-black p-3 md:p-6 flex flex-col justify-between speed-lines">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 font-mono text-[8px] md:text-[9px] uppercase">
              <span class="border-2 border-black p-2 bg-[#e9e8d8]">Negocio</span>
              <span class="border-2 border-black p-2 bg-[#e9e8d8]">Usuario</span>
              <span class="border-2 border-black p-2 bg-[#e9e8d8]">Datos</span>
              <span class="border-2 border-black p-2 bg-black text-white">Sistema</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#e9e8d8] border-y-[3px] border-black py-4">
